lead_paragraph: The Yankees’ feud with StubHub over the team’s new ticket policies may have taken a turn toward cooling when StubHub’s president reached out to the Yankees’ president.

headline.print_headline: Yankees Willing to Hold Meeting With StubHub
headline.main: Yankees Willing to Hold Meeting With StubHub

snippet: The Yankees’ feud with StubHub over the team’s new ticket policies may have taken a turn toward cooling when StubHub’s president reached out to the Yankees’ president.
abstract: New York Yankees president Randy Levine agrees to meet with third-party ticket sellers like StubHub to discuss dispute over team's new, more restrictive ticket policies.
